This paper deals with enhancing information dissemination in dynamic wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The use of beamforming and stability measures also suggests a focus on signal processing (cs.SI) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of algorithms and simulation results suggest a focus on machine learning (cs.MA) and data structures (cs.DS).
